<div class="post"><div class="posttop"><div class="username">Merrick ap'Milandra</div><div class="date">September 15th, 2010, 03:19 PM</div></div><div class="posttext">I've been talking with someone about both the vagaries of religion and various portions of the U.S. military actions in numerous countries including the middle east and, of course, the topic of the Qur'an came up so we started talking about people we knew who were Islamic and practiced Islam as a religion and I had a completely different opinion of them that this person had.<br />
